<refnamediv><refname>dnn_decode_classification</refname><refpurpose>Decode classification scores into top predictions.</refpurpose></refnamediv>
<refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>result = dnn_decode_classification(scores, labels, k, applySoftmax)</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv>
<refsection><title>Description</title><para><function>dnn_decode_classification</function> returns a struct with top scores, indices, and optional labels.</para></refsection>
<refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
result = dnn_decode_classification([0.1; 0.8; 0.2], ["a"; "b"; "c"], 2, %t);
]]></programlisting></refsection>
